  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tricycle fare reduction",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The All Sri Lankan Tricycle Owners Association said that with the reduction in fuel price, the second kilometer charge has been reduced from Rs.100 to Rs.90.",
        "Its president Sudil Jayaruk said that the existing fee of Rs 100 for the first kilometer cannot be changed in any way."
      ],
